Diamond::
She turned and smiled. "Yes, most bots are from 6 feet to 12 feet 
tall.  Your very large compared to most bots around." She smiled at 
him. "But that will give you an advantage. You seem so much stronger 
than the other bots here." she said in a softer voice. 

She guided the pod along it's flight plan. She would reach the base 
shortly.
